|  | m\_{f}(r,s,D)=\int\_{S\_{p}(r)}\lambda\_{D}(f)~{}\sigma\_{p}-\int\_{S\_{p}(s)}\lambda% \_{D}(f)~{}\sigma\_{p}. |  |

